Text: Compelling small cap investment opportunity As a registered Multex Investor member we will occasionally contact you with special opportunities provided by our partners To unsubscribe to this or any other exclusive offers please see the bottom of this message If youd like to learn more about Multex Investor please visit welcomeasp If you cant remember your Multex Investor password andor your user name click here lostinfoasp If you want to update your email address please click on the URL edituinfoasp To remove yourself from the mailing list for Special Promotions please REPLY to THIS email message with the word UNSUBSCRIBE in the subject line You may also unsubscribe on the account update page at edituinfoasp
